{
  "stem": "21349.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wrote to this person in-- whom I found on the picture, [INAUDIBLE] is his name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he sent me right away an affidavit on the school and said, you have been accepted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Come here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I needed a visa or a passport, I hadn't-- had neither.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said to me or they said to me, go to the American consul or go to the Canadian consul in Montreal and talk to them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to the British consulate first, because Canada was a dominion at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told them the whole story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said-- I said to him, I came to Canada legally, you see, with a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said to me, you have no passport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the Hebrew-- the Jewish agency can give you an affidavit in your passport and I make it to extend it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your passport is only good 'til April.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And according to the law, it expires two months before you have to apply for a new one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That you have to do as soon as you come to Montreal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, making a long story short, I got permission to go to the United States [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from-- from-- from September 'til February.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got permission to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now the next question was, how do I get money to get to the United States?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So-- so the Hebrew Immigrant Aid Society gave me $30 and I went by Greyhound bus.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went by Greyhound bus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left on the 7th-- or the 6th or 7th of September.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next day, Canada declared war, because the war broke out in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
